{"tid":1434121,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"叫內地學生「支那」 傳澳洲港留學生被打到入院","createTime":"2019-08-08T16:23:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T17:33:16.000Z","uid":39464,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c6a758ad5dec9f019f23ca4d17c13c1bf42aa5e8","tid":1434121,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T16:23:43.000Z","msg":"本港「反修例」風波持續，澳洲昆士蘭大學上月底有香港留學生在校園設「連儂牆」，表達對事件的關注，遭大批內地留學生襲擊、辱罵及恐嚇，澳洲華文網媒「今日墨爾本」則報道，澳洲墨爾本蒙納許大學(Monash University)克萊頓(Clayton)校區周二有二十多名香港留學生，在校內戴上頭盔、護目鏡等裝備遊行，表示要「保護我們的獨立的法律體系」，並強調「我們並非支持港獨」，惹內地留學生不滿，爭執期間有一名女生大叫「支那人可以冷靜一點嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n早前翻牆「出征」反修例陣營Facebook打「愛國戰」的內地網軍「帝吧」，今日在微博引述微信朋友圈消息指，涉事「港獨廢青」已被「暴躁老哥」起底並「上門毆打」，目前「躺在皇家墨爾本醫院」，又指該學生是位「老哥」，讀「MelUni(墨爾本大學)」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2019/8/1565250616_lh-1280w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2019%2F8%2F1565250616_lh-1280w.jpg&h=e9355955&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2019/8/1565250613_9J-1280w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2019%2F8%2F1565250613_9J-1280w.jpg&h=8c8f5315&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2019/8/1565250619_vQ-1280w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2019%2F8%2F1565250619_vQ-1280w.jpg&h=095a332d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2019/8/1565250621_82-1280w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2019%2F8%2F1565250621_82-1280w.jpg&h=d2f8682b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%e5%8f%ab%e5%85%a7%e5%9c%b0%e5%ad%b8%e7%94%9f%e3%80%8c%e6%94%af%e9%82%a3%e3%80%8d-%e5%82%b3%e6%be%b3%e6%b4%b2%e6%b8%af%e7%95%99%e5%ad%b8%e7%94%9f%e8%a2%ab%e6%89%93%e5%88%b0%e5%85%a5%